Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.72,0:01:31.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.76,0:01:32.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nee-san…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.70,0:01:34.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’m Para-sama’s pair!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.84,0:01:36.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,To put me with Alti at this point…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.78,0:01:40.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is all for the sake of regaining\N Chor Tempest’s honour.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.54,0:01:46.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.29,0:01:48.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,That’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.08,0:01:51.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why is their prayer having \Nno effect on the Simoun Gem?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.04,0:01:52.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Kaimu!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.84,0:01:53.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nee-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:55.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don’t call me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.34,0:01:57.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do {\i1}not{\i0} call me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.34,0:02:03.35,Titles,,90,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Reason
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.98,0:02:23.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Prayer?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.03,0:02:27.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, the chariots of the gods are activated by the prayers of the Simoun sibyllae.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.93,0:02:31.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Two priestesses unite their hearts in praise of Tempus Spatium.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:40.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,To reject one’s pair \Nis to reject the Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.30,0:02:48.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is unbelievable.\N I’ve never heard of such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.52,0:02:50.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,All of this is guesswork.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.82,0:02:57.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,But thanks to the two of you, we’ve discovered a hidden aspect of the Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:03:01.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,You’ve done well, although you probably don’t appreciate my saying so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.00,0:03:09.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,So that means… that I probably won’t be able to pair… with Nee-san any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.54,0:03:14.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,You understand, don’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.94,0:03:30.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,The enemy hasn’t shown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.06,0:03:35.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,We’ve been lying around so much that I’m almost gathering dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.58,0:03:42.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,So would you rather be fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:44.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,I didn’t say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.37,0:03:46.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,I just meant that \Nthere’s nothing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.62,0:03:50.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,You should consider your words carefully,\Nor else keep them to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.58,0:03:57.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ahhhhhh! I’m just {\i1}soooo{\i0} bored!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:09.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rodoreamon can get really scary when she’s mad. I’m gonna stay out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.64,0:04:19.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,What are you thinking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:21.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Something other than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.62,0:04:25.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.11,0:04:27.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Maajon?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:31.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it’s the greatest Ri Maajon that a Simoun can perform.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.16,0:04:34.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s said it can bring about \Nthe ultimate miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.76,0:04:36.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ultimate…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.63,0:04:41.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,You were imitating the\N Emerald Ri Maajon on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.94,0:04:44.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just how do you think Neviril \Nwould feel if she saw that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.56,0:04:48.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh? Did I do some kind of Ri Maajon?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.39,0:04:52.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, so {\i1}that’s{\i0} what that was about!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.43,0:04:54.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.69,0:04:56.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.94,0:04:59.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Tell me, what would happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.48,0:05:03.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I’m afraid I’ve never seen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.00,0:05:05.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wapourif, didn’t Neviril and Amuria—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.08,0:05:20.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril and Amuria did \Nthe Emerald Ri Maajon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.41,0:05:21.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.90,0:05:24.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,I get it! They tried but\N they couldn’t do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:28.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.09,0:05:31.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see. So she and Amuria…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.60,0:05:52.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wow, you’re so thorough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:57.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Tempus Spatium likes cleanliness and shuns places that are dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.60,0:06:04.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,My mother always said that a dirty kitchen or bathroom brings misfortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.66,0:06:08.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,You’re amazing, Mamiina! \NYou know a lot that I don’t.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.89,0:06:11.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Maybe it suits me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.14,0:06:14.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Cooking and cleaning like this, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:18.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Being here has felt like a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.70,0:06:23.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ah, it’s stuck and it won’t come off. If only we could get citrus fruit…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.50,0:06:24.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Citrus fruit?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.90,0:06:26.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,The acid in the juice\N would dissolve the stain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.36,0:06:29.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,You really {\i1}are{\i0} amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:51.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.61,0:07:04.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.15,0:07:08.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do the Emerald Ri Maajon with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.16,0:07:17.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru, what are you—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.91,0:07:20.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,I get it! You and Amuria failed at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:27.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,But with me, I bet you can do it. Come on, Neviril, let’s try the Em—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.09,0:07:28.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.60,0:07:37.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.64,0:07:39.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’ll go get a mop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.27,0:07:44.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:46.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Drop it, Aaeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.15,0:07:47.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.24,0:07:48.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,That topic is…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:53.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because it makes her\N remember Amuria’s death?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:06.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.60,0:08:16.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,That was in spectacularly bad taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:19.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Poor Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:28.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,I never met Amuria, but you shouldn’t speak ill of the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:31.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,What? I didn’t—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:32.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,C’mere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.84,0:08:38.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.56,0:08:54.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why’d you drag me \Nall the way down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.98,0:08:58.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sheesh! Tell me, do you {\i1}like{\i0} Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.85,0:09:00.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sure, I like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.62,0:09:02.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,That’s not what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.08,0:09:03.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.36,0:09:08.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do you wanna talk with her as long as \Nyou can? Feel her warmth as you hold her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.56,0:09:12.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you filled with love and desire for her? That kind of “like,” I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.24,0:09:13.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sure, I want Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.22,0:09:18.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can fly higher with her\N than with anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:22.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:27.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,How did that feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.23,0:09:28.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,How did what feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.32,0:09:29.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,What I just did!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.80,0:09:32.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, we’re not about to fly into battle, so it’s kind of weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.63,0:09:37.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you really {\i1}liked{\i0} someone, \Nyou’d feel differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.64,0:09:42.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril {\i1}like{\i0}-liked Amuria that way. Get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.40,0:09:45.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,What does that have to do \Nwith the Emerald Ri Maajon?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.69,0:09:48.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s a lot better if you \N{\i1}like{\i0} each other, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.28,0:09:56.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.20,0:10:00.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.20,0:10:03.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.29,0:10:07.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.14,0:10:11.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:19.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’ll be all right… \Nif you do that with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.62,0:10:23.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,We can do it, if we’re together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.10,0:10:44.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Maajon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.24,0:10:54.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because… because it makes her remember Amuria’s death.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.06,0:10:59.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nooooooooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:02.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril, what’s going on? Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.88,0:11:04.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.94,0:11:07.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:42.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’ll open the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:50.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s dusty in here, but this must be better than sharing a room with Aaeru—with the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.90,0:11:53.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.54,0:11:59.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Get some rest, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.70,0:12:25.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Maajon…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.00,0:12:29.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,It must be really great.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.22,0:12:30.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.49,0:12:33.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to try it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.44,0:12:35.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,With Dominura?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.60,0:12:38.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,It doesn’t matter\N who my partner is…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.70,0:12:41.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do you {\i1}like{\i0} Dominura?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.32,0:12:44.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don’t know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.45,0:12:50.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,They say if you really {\i1}like{\i0} somebody, you want to kiss her even when you’re not flying a Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.72,0:12:55.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Apparently, a lot of things \Nare better if you {\i1}like{\i0} your pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.68,0:12:57.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,A lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.09,0:12:59.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yep. A lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.38,0:13:13.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,What did Central Command say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.43,0:13:16.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,{They said that }Unless the enemy shows signs of activity,\Nwe should just watch them for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.94,0:13:20.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,That enemy base ship was almost impossible to find.\NDo they think we should just leave it alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.98,0:13:26.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,They’ve apparently been distracted by unexpected problems with the {\i1}Arcus Prima{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.95,0:13:34.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,As I thought, they’re missing the forest for the trees. \NIf things go on this way, our Holy Land will…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.48,0:13:41.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Dominura, you look uneasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.55,0:13:45.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,It may be out of line for a man in my position to offer advice to a sibylla, but—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.92,0:13:47.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, it certainly is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.00,0:14:03.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Limone, what is it? \NIs something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.94,0:14:05.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.20,0:14:11.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,How did that feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.49,0:14:16.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Did you feel that you {\i1}liked{\i0} me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.86,0:14:26.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Run along.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.78,0:14:44.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Amuria… is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.88,0:14:46.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.66,0:14:49.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:51.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:55.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,I finally found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.46,0:15:01.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,W-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.52,0:15:03.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Whew!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.04,0:15:04.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,What are you…?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.67,0:15:06.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.44,0:15:16.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,C’mon, look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.72,0:15:24.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,You can’t feel the wind in here. It’s so stuffy and full of old junk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.68,0:15:28.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,There’s nothing here but\N a bunch of useless memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.41,0:15:33.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let’s go outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:39.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Come on, let’s open\N the door together, Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.08,0:15:43.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.82,0:16:00.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.34,0:16:08.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, that hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.07,0:16:11.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril is tired. Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.24,0:16:12.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,What? But…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.53,0:16:13.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.88,0:16:31.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril, I don’t think Aaeru\N means any harm, but—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.92,0:16:37.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,I would like to sleep \Nfor a while. Is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.25,0:17:05.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where’s Aaeru?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.50,0:17:06.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.88,0:17:10.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,That was surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.04,0:17:11.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.24,0:17:13.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Not just for Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.04,0:17:20.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,The rest of us have avoided \Ntalking about it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.62,0:17:24.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,I felt that mentioning it\N would keep us from moving on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.44,0:17:28.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Amuria was strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.48,0:17:33.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,She was always aiming higher, and never doubted herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:38.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, I thought the war \Nwas too much for me but…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.18,0:17:45.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,When Amuria was with us, \Nit felt like we were invincible,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.66,0:17:49.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,so I was afraid to admit\N that she was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.78,0:17:54.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, even now I don’t want to. But—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.02,0:18:05.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,What happened to my…?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.18,0:18:08.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,You caught me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.69,0:18:10.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,What’s up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.64,0:18:15.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,What is {\i1}that{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.56,0:18:25.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,What sort of creature \Nis {\i1}that{\i0} supposed to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:26.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, that’s funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.28,0:18:31.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Come on! I sewed it as well as I could!\N I know it’s a bit ugly, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.17,0:18:33.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Its face is all misshapen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.00,0:18:37.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s fine. This is adorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.67,0:18:41.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s certainly unique… just like its maker.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.39,0:18:42.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.88,0:19:03.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,I didn’t mean to hurt Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.42,0:19:08.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,I just thought that we could do anything if we were together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.96,0:19:10.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,How can you be so confident?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:16.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Haven’t you ever felt despair?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.82,0:19:20.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,If I told you, \Nwhat difference would it make?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.25,0:19:30.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Maybe it was a mistake \Nto entrust Neviril to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.28,0:19:44.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,We can’t wait for the brass any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.10,0:19:48.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,We should scout out the base ship while the enemy remains quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.34,0:19:51.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril, Aaeru, it’s up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.60,0:19:54.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wait, those two are…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.21,0:19:59.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,The two of them are the best pair in Chor Tempest at the moment. Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.70,0:20:00.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,But…!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.32,0:20:05.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominura, I can’t pair\N with Aaeru right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.32,0:20:09.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, you said\Nthe Simoun are—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.56,0:20:11.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, and that is why.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:16.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,People’s feelings aren’t toys!\N How can you just assume—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.60,0:20:17.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.69,0:20:21.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:29.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril, I guess you don’t want to, but I…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.86,0:20:36.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril, please consider the interests of the nation above all else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.58,0:20:40.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,We are Simoun sibyllae.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.84,0:21:12.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.86,0:21:22.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,— This is pointless.\N— It’s not pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.62,0:21:27.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Not pointless at all.\N We can fly. We can!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.03,0:21:44.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Their prayer seems \Nto have been heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.74,0:21:47.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,I guess feelings\N don’t matter after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.74,0:21:53.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,They do matter. \NWe must conclude that Neviril…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.92,0:21:55.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.02,0:22:05.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.76,0:22:11.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was right. You do want me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.44,0:22:17.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,You can fly with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.48,0:22:19.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Anything is possible\N when you’re with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.16,0:22:23.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do I want Aaeru?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.88,0:22:28.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, it can’t be. I’m… I’m…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.60,0:22:34.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’m… afraid of Aaeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.92,0:24:06.59,Titles,,85,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.59,0:24:11.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you ordering me to dismantle a Simoun, Sibylla Dominura?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.09,0:24:15.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next time, on Simoun:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.00,0:24:18.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,That Which Must Not Be Violated.
